177 A.3d 128 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. K.D., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER. IN THE MATTER OF THE GUARDIANSHIP OF S.S., MINOR-RESPONDENT.

C-435 September Term 2017

079818 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2651/5513-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
